\end_inset

).
 Green is positive, red is negative, and gray is zero.
 
\series bold
b
\series default
, The transient pathway effectively combines a positive channel that leads
 the sustained pathway by 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau$
\end_inset

 and a negative channel that lags by 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau$
\end_inset

.
 
\series bold
